OL,3,CRE and prayer in NI schools
OL,4,C'unlawful,' Supreme Court rules
OL,6,FThe provision of religious education
OL,7,Fand collective worship in Northern
OL,8,FIreland schools does not comply with
OL,9,Fhuman rights standards and is
OL,10,Funlawful, the UK Supreme Court has
OL,11,Fruled.
OL,13,FIn a landmark judgment, the court
OL,14,Fupheld an appeal brought by a pupil at
OL,15,Fa Belfast school and her father, and
OL,16,Freinstated an earlier court ruling
OL,17,Fthat the teaching of RE breaches human
OL,18,Frights as it does not approach the
OL,19,Fsubject in an "objective, critical and
OL,20,Fpluralist manner".
