OL,3,CRE and prayer in NI schools
OL,4,C'unlawful,' Supreme Court rules
OL,6,FHer parents wrote a letter to the
OL,7,Fschool voicing concerns that their
OL,8,Fdaughter's education did not appear to
OL,9,Fconform with their own religious and
OL,10,Fphilosophical convictions.
OL,12,FIn a reply, the school confirmed its
OL,13,Fprovision of religious education and
OL,14,Fcollective worship was "Bible-based"
OL,15,Fand that it followed the core syllabus
OL,16,Ffor education.
OL,18,FJR87 and her father, known as G,
OL,19,Fchallenged the legality of this and
OL,20,Fsought judicial review against the
OL,21,FDepartment of Education.
