OL,6,FHowever, this was overturned by the
OL,7,FCourt of Appeal, so the family took
OL,8,Ftheir case to the Supreme Court.
OL,10,FIn a unanimous judgment delivered on
OL,11,FWednesday, the UK's highest court
OL,12,Fallowed the appeal brought by JR87 and
OL,13,FG and dismissed a cross-appeal brought
OL,14,Fby the department.
