OL,3,CRE and prayer in NI schools
OL,4,C'unlawful,' Supreme Court rules
OL,6,FDelivering the judgment, Lord Stephens
OL,7,Fsaid: "The Court of Appeal was wrong
OL,8,Fin its application of established
OL,9,Fprinciples of ECHR law and should not
OL,10,Fhave departed from the (High Court)
OL,11,Fjudge's finding that the parents had
OL,12,Fvalid concerns in relation to
OL,13,Fwithdrawing JR87 from religious
OL,14,Feducation and collective worship.
OL,16,F"Furthermore, the Court of Appeal fell
OL,17,Finto error in making a distinction
OL,18,Fbetween indoctrination and the state
OL,19,Fconveying information or knowledge in
OL,20,Fa manner which was not objective,
OL,21,Fcritical, and pluralistic.
OL,26,@oD@GOUxD@AOU
