OL,6,F"The concepts are two sides of the
OL,7,Fsame coin: conveying knowledge in a
OL,8,Fmanner that is not objective,
OL,9,Fcritical, and pluralistic amounts to
OL,10,Fpursuing the aim of indoctrination."
OL,12,FLord Stephens also said the Court of
OL,13,FAppeal ought to have found that having
OL,14,Fto withdraw JR87 from religious
OL,15,Feducation was "capable of placing an
OL,16,Fundue burden" on her parents.
