OL,6,FResponding to the judgment, Darragh
OL,7,FMackin of Phoenix Law, solicitor for
OL,8,FJR87 and her father, said it was a
OL,9,F"watershed moment" for educational
OL,10,Frights.
OL,12,FHe said: "The Supreme Court has
OL,13,Fconfirmed that all children are
OL,14,Fentitled to an education that respects
OL,15,Ftheir freedom of thought, conscience,
OL,16,Fand religion.
OL,18,F"The judgment makes clear that the
OL,19,FState cannot rely on withdrawal
OL,20,Fmechanisms to justify religious
OL,21,Finstruction.
